{"tid":1734332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非救Poly救命必做三件事！","createTime":"2019-11-18T10:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:01:27.000Z","uid":93324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45b2d910a9e2c79257c7fd2353d21edd9ec93f7d","tid":1734332,"uid":93324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"和理非，知道大家都好無助，但係無助唔係唔做嘢嘅藉口。廢話少講，<strong>如果你真心係想拯救Poly嘅手足，請做下面三項動作，好安全，唔會拉唔使死。</strong><br />\n<br />\n(1) 國際陣線復活：必須以正視聽，<strong>人地美國咁大個國家唔係得人權法一道板斧</strong>，1989年中美蜜月期都尚且制裁咗中共三年，依家2019年中國威脅論甚囂塵上，美國成班對華鷹派虎視眈眈，一定唔會就咁算數。所以，我地國際陣線高人，準備咗以下Tweet比大家Tweet：<br />\n<br />\n‪<strong>Berlin Blockade happening in Hong Kong right under your eyes! The regime is laying siege to a uni plotting to starve all inside to death. Journalists denied entry and medics arrested on dubious riot charges. Our desperate plea for a US Berlin Airlift!‬</strong><br />\n<br />\nTag: @SolomonYue, @HawleyMO, @marcorubio, @tedcruz, @senatemajldr, @realDonaldTrump, @JoeBiden, @SecPompeo, @SenSchumer, @CECCgov<br />\n<br />\n<strong>十大美國對港最高決策人，缺一不可！隨便再加</strong><br />\n<br />\n(2) 針對泛民施壓：越來越人話泛民想區選前食人血饅頭，泛民你地澄清嘅機會到了，<strong>請大家去各大泛民議員fb留言，要求佢地全體議員立即前往Poly斡旋，再唔係一陣遊行就一定要打頭陣，呢個時候我地最需要團結！</strong><br />\nLink:<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ixx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=724e86f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/</a><br />\n民主黨<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thedphk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthedphk%2F&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ixx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=c9e76158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/thedphk/</a><br />\n民主派會議召集人&lrm;: &lrm;毛孟靜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ClaudiaMoManChing/\" data-sr-u